I will do it.
To confirm, you still want that mutux, and just change flag to atomic. 
It will be slow, but should be still fine since it only initialize once.

```
atomic<bool> b;
if(!b.load(acquire))
{
lock()
if(!b.load(acquire))
 initialize;
 b.store(true, release);
}
unlock();
} 
```
-L

